Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.74,0:00:45.55,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(650,0)}{\pos(246,160)}{\fs48}伊諾肯迪斯七世
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.36,0:00:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好臭
